service.name: Status Resolution Support Services Payment
service.description: Status Resolution Support Services (SRSS) payment is a  support payment for eligible recipients who are awaiting resolution of their immigration status. The payment comprises a Living Allowance, Rental Assistance Allowance and Dependent Child Allowance. The SRSS payment is paid under the Financial Management and Accountability Act 1997 rather than social security law.
